<div class=3D"wp-block-uagb-advanced-heading uagb-block-8778e174"><h2 class=
=3D"uagb-heading-text"><strong>Area of a Sector =E2=80=93 Definition, Formu=
las, and Calculator</strong></h2></div>



<div class=3D"wp-block-uagb-separator uagb-block-711b7707"><div class=3D"ua=
gb-separator-spacing-wrapper"><div class=3D"wp-block-uagb-separator__inner"=
